  <md:abstract><para>By the end of this section, you will be able to:</para><list>
<item>Identify phenomena in which electromagnetic waves behave like a beam of photons and particles behave like waves</item>
<item>Describe the physics principles behind electron microscopy</item>
<item>Summarize the evolution of scientific thought that led to the development of quantum mechanics</item>
</list></md:abstract>
